      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on the app store page for our new puzzle game \"Neon Prism\" and i need a killer description. we're trying to hit the trending page and the algorithm is kind of stupid—it basically just ranks based on a \"hype score.\" \n\nthe score is calculated like this:\n`score = count(\"!\") + count([\"amazing\", \"incredible\", \"unbelievable\", \"fun\", \"exciting\"])`\n\ncan you write a description for the game that gets the score as high as possible? the game is just a neon-colored prism puzzle game where you match shapes to clear levels. make it really loud and hype so we rank high!",
